00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:36,240
weal and woe

264
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:39,020
with Lyu Jianwen.

265
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:41,510
♫I have passed by so many people♫

266
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,740
I will never break my promise.

267
00:21:41,740 --> 00:21:43,330
♫All that is left♫

268
00:21:43,360 --> 00:21:48,450
♫Is my reflection in your eyes♫

269
00:21:46,980 --> 00:21:48,220
I've remembered.

270
00:21:49,320 --> 00:21:51,080
I, Lyu Jianwen, vow to

271
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:53,710
be with Yan Rushan

272
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,240
for the rest of my life,

273
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:59,310
till death do us part.

274
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:08,720
Do you think I can live happily

275
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,360
if I forget you?

276
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:15,400
More than the pain of separation,

277
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,160
I'm more afraid of

278
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:20,640
losing the right to love you.

279
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:46,060
